messages.content: What is the purpose of the ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node?
The ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node is used to download models, including Checkpoints and LoRA, from external links in ComfyUI.
Does ComfyUI-ModelDownloader support downloading LoRA models?
Yes, the ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node supports downloading both Checkpoints and LoRA models.
Can ComfyUI-ModelDownloader be used as a standalone output node?
Yes, the ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node can act as a standalone output node in ComfyUI.
Is ComfyUI-ModelDownloader a custom node or a built-in node in ComfyUI?
ComfyUI-ModelDownloader is a custom node in ComfyUI.
What types of models can be downloaded using the ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node?
The ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node can download Checkpoints and LoRA models from external links.
Does the ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node require any additional plugins to function?
No, the ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node does not require any additional plugins to function, as it is a standalone custom node.
Is the ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node limited to specific model sources?
The ComfyUI-ModelDownloader node can download models from external links, so it is not limited to specific model sources.
